Director Seo…

15
00:02:08,795 --> 00:02:10,380
When did your memory come back?

16
00:02:12,883 --> 00:02:15,510
Did you even lose
your memory to begin with?

17
00:02:21,099 --> 00:02:23,101
If I hadn't lost my memory,

18
