51
00:05:43,593 --> 00:05:47,764
<i>If we keep this up,
who would trust us enough to work with us?</i>

52
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:50,559
<i>And, Jangseon,</i>

53
00:05:51,810 --> 00:05:55,564
<i>from now on,
