Keep that in mind.

193
00:18:36,949 --> 00:18:38,659
Or you'll regret it later.

194
00:18:38,743 --> 00:18:39,744
Ms. Cha…

195
00:18:44,206 --> 00:18:45,458
The matter with Seonu

196
00:18:46,042 --> 00:18:47,460
is about Daesan Group.

197
00:18:48,085 --> 00:18:51,005
