223
00:21:10,436 --> 00:21:12,480
If you trust me and follow my lead,

224
00:21:13,731 --> 00:21:15,566
I can make it possible.

225
00:21:20,112 --> 00:21:21,614
If you agree with me,

226
00:21:21,697 --> 00:21:23,616
